Package me.ashtheking.island

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IslandGen
    This is the main class of the project.
    Module
    The abstract class Module is key to IslandGen.
    ModuleHeight
    The class ModuleHeight is the default module.
    ModuleLoader
    ModuleLoader is responsible for loading and keeping track of all modules that are specified in "mods.config".
    ModuleMoisture
    ModuleMoisture generates a moisture map.
    ModuleSea
    ModuleSea generates a basic colored heightmap, and takes into account water and land.
    ModuleTemp
    ModuleTemp provides a temperature rendering the area.
